## Установка

### Maven

```xml
<repository>
    <id>jitpack.io</id>
    <url>https://jitpack.io</url>
</repository>

<dependency>
    <groupId>com.github.VolanDeMor1</groupId>
    <artifactId>EscapeTimeApi</artifactId>
    <version>1.2.4</version>
</dependency>
```

### Gradle

```gradle
repositories {
    maven("https://jitpack.io")
}
dependencies {
    implementation("com.github.VolanDeMor1:EscapeTimeApi:1.2.4")
}
```
